<HEADER>
A3064 &Cx1f; tab-z
r k BC-SLAVERY-TODAY-NYTSF &LR;      09-07 0969
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-SLAVERY-TODAY-NYTSF </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
THE HORRIFYING REALITY OF SLAVERY IN AFRICA TODAY 
</HEADLINE>
   (Commentary)  
<TEXT>
<P>
   (To purchase this ``separate buy'' article from the New York
Times Syndicate please contact syndicate sales representative DEBRA
WEYDERT at 732-390-4480)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; By DIANA BUTLER BASS &LR;  &QC; 
 &UR; (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) &LR;  &QC;
</P>
<P>
