<P>
   The fourth annual Earth Maui Nature Summit will be held Sept.
18-26 on, naturally, one of Hawaii's most beautiful islands. The
program is designed to foster an appreciation of Hawaii's natural
environment and host culture while encouraging protection of the
island's natural resources. Throughout the summit there will be
nature adventures, workshops and educational seminars. For
information, call 800-KAPALUA or write Kapalua Nature Society, 800
Kapalua Drive, Kapalua, Maui, Hawaii 96761.
</P>
