hurry. The result is The Working Cook, which debuts today. &HT;    This new column by staff writer Tara Duggan offers a three-prong
approach to everyday cooking. If you use all of Tara's suggestions,
a family of four can have meals on the table five nights a week.
Now &AMP; Later, is a recipe that serves 12; 30-Minute recipe takes a
half-hour or less of preparation time; and Fast 5 has just five
ingredients and can be on the table in 20 minutes or less.
