into the saucepan and add the remaining 11/2 cups milk. Taste and
add more salt if needed; heat and serve.
</P>
<P>
   Serves 4.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; PER SERVING: &LR;   &LR; 370 calories, &LR;   &LR; 17 g protein, 57 g
carbohydrate, &LR;   &LR; 12 g fat (6 g saturated), 37 mg cholesterol, 437 mg
sodium, 10 &LR;   &LR; g fiber. &LR;
</P>
</TEXT>
