injury, had neck surgery and was held out of contact until the Aug.
28 opener against Louisiana Tech (20 of 32, 242 yards, 2 TDs, 1
INT). He could be the key to the Seminoles' hopes. (Barnhart,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
