single ownership, many powerful media brands _ among them CBS, MTV,
The Nashville Network, Nickelodeon, Paramount, Simon &AMP; Schuster,
VH1 and, well, Blockbuster _ ranged from outrage to outright
acceptance. By Stuart Elliott.
</P>
<P>
   (The column is scheduled to move by 8:30 p.m. ET.)
</P>
<P>
   CREDIT (New York) _ Treasury yields rose Tuesday as investors
awaited an inflation report scheduled for release on Friday and
braced for speeches by Federal Reserve officials. By Robert
Hurtado.
</P>
<P>
   (The story has moved.)
</P>
