 &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
 &QL; 
The show: ``Get Real.'' &QL; 
What: Hour-long comedy-drama about the travails of the modern
family, seen through the eyes of three precocious teens. &QL; 
The stars &UR; : &LR;  Anne Hathaway, Jesse Eisenberg, Eric Christian Olsen,
Debrah Farentino, Jon Tenny, Christina Pickles. &QL; 
Where &UR; : &LR;  Fox. &QL; 
When &UR; : &LR;  2 stars &QL;
