Courtney, 6. It's one of the sport's most arresting sights: A
soccer player lunging under a streaking ball and blasting it with
their head into the opponent's net. But it's also a practice
attracting growing concern, especially for younger players, with
recent studies suggesting that the repeated blows to the head can
