<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-TRUMP-U.N.-NYT, which will move
in ``a'' news file.) 
c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``Rich people don't like losing their view _ that is pure and
simple what this is all about.''
</P>
<P>
   _DONALD TRUMP, the wealthy developer who faces oppostion to his
construction of the tallest residential tower in the world.
</P>
